rows.label: qev030610_MSG0001
rows.name:
Prone take mates sooner than other races.
I found Hexuna. Took liking to her.
We married next day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030610_MSG0002
rows.name:
Thoughts and feelings in moment are only truth.
Remember this, Earth alien. You lose what is dear
if you think too long.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030610_MSG1001
rows.name: Ha! Drunken tests of strength have turned into fights![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030610_MSG1002
rows.name:
Happy brawl like this is true Prone way.
Better than fretting over Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030610_MSG2001
rows.name:
Are you enjoying rite of marriage?
It makes me remember day I wed Hexuna.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030610_MSG2002
rows.name:
She had rough time preparing today's feast.
I should find special treat for her.[ST:wait ]
